 ...sl-imx8qm-lpddr4-arm2-jdi-wuxga-lvds1-panel.dts |    8 ++++++++
 .../fsl-imx8qm-mek-jdi-wuxga-lvds1-panel.dts       |    8 ++++++++
 2 files changed, 16 insertions(+)

